1.1.1.1
log
@import of pork 0.5.0

pork is a programmable, ncurses-based AIM client that mostly looks and
feels like ircII.

From Jolan "it's been tested on i386, sparc, macppc, and sparc64" Luff
<jolan AT cryptonomicon DOT org>
